  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PeruTM7.9">
<l>kuṉṟi ṉāṟkuṭai kavittatuṅ kōlak kuravai kōtta tuṅkuṭa māṭṭum</l>
<l>kaṉṟi ṉālviḷa veṟintatuṅ kālāṟ kāḷi yaṉṟalai mitittatum mutalā</l>
<l>veṉṟi cērpiḷḷai nalviḷai yāṭṭa maṉaitti lumaṅkeṉ ṉuḷḷamuḷ kuḷira</l>
<l>oṉṟuṅ kaṇṭiṭap peṟṟilē ṉaṭiyēṉ kāṇu māṟiṉi yuṇṭeṉi laruḷē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>I, who am a servant, did not get to see anything [being] there,</l>
<l>so that my heart feels refreshed inside:</l>
<l rend="indent">none of the children’s good games endowed with victory starting from</l>
<l rend="indent">[Your] spreading an umbrella with the hill,</l>
<l rend="indent">[Your] performing the beautiful kuravai-dance  and the dance with waterpots,</l>
<l rend="indent">[Your] smashing the wood-apple tree with a calf,</l>
<l rend="indent">and [Your] treading on Kāliya’s head with the feet!</l>
<l>If there is a means for me [who am a servant], to see [all that], [do] bestow [it upon me].</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
